Notes.Text:
This update for libqt5-qtbase fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2023-51714: Fixed an incorrect integer overflow check (bsc#1218413).

Vulnerabilities.Description: An issue was discovered in the HTTP2 implementation in Qt before 5.15.17, 6.x before 6.2.11, 6.3.x through 6.5.x before 6.5.4, and 6.6.x before 6.6.2. network/access/http2/hpacktable.cpp has an incorrect HPack integer overflow check.
